name: Warui
description:
Warui
Is the personification of Me, Getting into NFT.
I was working for the concept of my own NFT, and all of the sudden I got sick. And we all knew what happen in the world for the past couple year (really not good). And I almost dropped the whole NFT thing because of it, but thankfully I got a friend who encourage me and giving me spirit to keep moving forward.
Funny enough, I recovering when I release my first NFT.
I hope Warui Onee-san is getting well soon too...
